<h2>Button Shortcodes</h2>
<p>
  You can easily add buttons to the page using [button]. For example: <br>
  <pre>
   <code>
    [button url="http://google.com" color="white" text="Hello, World!"]
   </code>
  </pre>
  <br>
  This would output a white button that links to google.com with the text of "Hello, World!".
</p>

<h3>
  Available Colors:
</h3>
<ul>
  <li>
    yellow
  </li>
  <li>
    white
  </li>
  <li>
    drkpurple
  </li>
</ul>
